flowchart LR

A[Full Conversation History]

A --> B{Context Too Large?}

B -->|No| C[Send to LLM]

B -->|Yes| D[Split Context]

D --> E[Recent Messages]
D --> F[Older Messages]

F --> G[Summarize / Compress]

G --> H[Compressed Summary]

H --> I[Rebuild Context]

E --> I

I --> J[New Prompt to LLM]

